| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-5654 — Recovery Inhibition (incransom)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8e41db9c-97a9-57ec-92cb-421919c8385f"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
